quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  40,67,"Ko Kaŋko woni takɗo on e mbumbuldi, refti e toɓɓere (maniiyu), refti e heɗɗere, refti o yaltiniri on penuuɓe fii no njottoron cemmbe mon, e no laatoron nayeeɓe, - no e mo'on, ƴettiteteeɓe ado ɗuum, - haa no njottoron lajal kappaangal, mbelajo'o, on kaqqilay."
  40,68,"Ko Kaŋko woni guurnoowo e waroowo. Si O haajii e fiyaaku, ko O wi'anat mo tan: "Laato", o laatoo."
  40,69,"E a tinaani, ɓeen yeddondirteeɓe e aayeeje Allah ɗeen, ko honno ɓe pirlitoraa?"
  40,70,"Ɓeen yedduɓe deftere ndeen, e kon ko Min nuliri nulaaɓe Amen ɓeen; ɓe ngaray anndude,"
  40,71,"tuma kolombooje ɗen mbaɗoyaa e daaɗe maɓɓe, e jolokooje(callalle) ɗeen, hara heɓe ndaasiree"
  40,72,"ka ndeer ngulɗam; refti ɓe huɓɓoyee ka ndeer Yiite."
  40,73,"refti ɓe mbi'anee: "Ko holto woni ɗin ɗi kafidatnoɗon?"
  40,74,"Ko aldah e Allah?" Ɓe mbi'a: "Ɗi majjitike min. Wurin, min ngonaano ko adii, e dewugol hay hu'unde". Ko hona nih Allah majjinirta he'eferɓe ɓen."
  40,75,"Ko waɗi on ɗuum, ko ko mbeltoratnoɗon kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko mbliratnoɗon kon."
  40,76,"Naatiree dame Jahannama ɗeen, luttugol ton. nge bonii jaaƴorde wona'de mawnintiniiɓe ɓeen!."
  40,77,"Muñño. Pellet, fodoore Allah nden, ko goonga. Ko si Min hollete yoga e ko Min podi ɓe kon, maa hara Min ƴettite (ado mum) ko ka Amen ɓe ruttirtee."